/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f250c2bdb7323ce706b77aab1923e564691bb6e","tid":2056042,"uid":21602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"獨立post掃盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee28fcc808a6c7621a2e8bafdd2d1c63b79f4d0","tid":2056042,"uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"仲有一個好嚴重嘅邏輯問題<br />\n你以前無民主,宜家比以前更民主<br />\n你以前無, 宜家都唔可以有<br />\n<br />\n以前民怨細；宜家民怨大<br />\n以前物價,樓價地價低；宜家嘜都拎世界第1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 194幾年美國買香港塊地幾十萬,今日有6座豪宅估價都過百億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前帝制奴隸制, 宜家具中共特色新型奴隸制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國思維 = 強盗邏輯 + 強姦犯邏輯"},{"pid":"6d35dd3a29dbdd968511f2bdcc158dcad2bb2364","tid":2056042,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"樓主咁正常 懷疑佢俾人kack咗 麻煩admin做嘢"},{"pid":"09bdd79ad96b813a550a64763ed2f617e739b8cc","tid":2056042,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"諗吓92年台海導彈危機就知完全合理<br />\n台灣呢個有完整軍隊有天險幾千萬人口既國家都差d開波 唔係第七艦隊駛黎都唔知會點<br />\n仲要果陣既中共已經係算温和扮豬期<br />\n對比五六十年代 一窮二白冇野好輸 好戰既中共 香港有選舉絕對會打"},{"pid":"2fd6e3f2dac5b19f38d7cee08bfb7ec6d5ae2d35","tid":2056042,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"華大媽今朝先插完英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36e396aefb5da66ca41736983201e167766f7be","tid":2056042,"uid":202724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a2138b93dfb964d7a2a3760726b0ccedb43957","tid":2056042,"uid":188282,"like":